00:20:19.579 --> 00:20:24.939
to solve for so many things, and it's extremely rectangular in its format, there are limitations

00:20:24.939 --> 00:20:31.660
to that. And if you want to know the causality of why something is happening at a role level,

00:20:31.660 --> 00:20:36.300
and you want to say, okay, this particular person in these, you know, the top decile,

00:20:36.300 --> 00:20:40.540
